      <title>Milei 成立 Aerolineas 和 YPF 进行阿根廷私有化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/milei-sets-up-aerolineas-and-ypf-for-privatization-in-argentina</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统哈维尔·米莱迈出了阿根廷国营企业私有化的第一步，颁布了一项全面的法令，为私营企业控制关键部门打开了大门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/milei-sets-up-aerolineas-and-ypf-for-privatization-in-argentina</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 02:37:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚拒绝美国加入红海海军行动的请求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/australia-rejects-us-request-to-join-red-sea-naval-operation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚拒绝了美国派遣军舰帮助保护红海国际航道的请求，国防部长理查德·马勒斯表示，澳大利亚的战略重点必须留在印度-太平洋地区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/australia-rejects-us-request-to-join-red-sea-naval-operation</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 02:02:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>格雷厄姆表示，如果中国试图入侵台湾，他将起草制裁措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/us-senator-plans-china-sanctions-from-hell-for-a-taiwan-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议员林赛·格雷厄姆表示，如果中国试图入侵台湾，他将帮助起草对中国实施的制裁措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/us-senator-plans-china-sanctions-from-hell-for-a-taiwan-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 00:39:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Milei 推出广泛改革以自由化阿根廷经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/milei-announces-sweeping-reforms-to-deregulate-argentina-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统哈维尔·米莱宣布进行全面改革，以减少国家对阿根廷经济的控制，包括采取企业私有化、促进出口和结束价格管制等措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/milei-announces-sweeping-reforms-to-deregulate-argentina-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 00:29:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金正恩称洲际弹道导弹发出核反应警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/kim-jong-un-says-icbm-launch-conveys-warning-of-nuclear-response</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜领导人金正恩表示，朝鲜本周发射洲际弹道导弹发出警告，如果其拥有核武器的敌人挑衅，平壤将以核攻击回应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/kim-jong-un-says-icbm-launch-conveys-warning-of-nuclear-response</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 00:19:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度备受争议的印度教寺庙为更多寺庙打开“闸门”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/india-s-controversial-hindu-temple-opens-floodgates-for-more</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪准备在一座有数百年历史的清真寺所在地开设一座有争议的印度教寺庙时，印度教团体在过去一周赢得了法院对其他有争议的宗教场所的重要裁决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-21/india-s-controversial-hindu-temple-opens-floodgates-for-more</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Dec 2023 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西国会让哈达德 2024 年财政赤字接近于零</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/brazil-congress-gets-haddad-closer-to-zero-2024-fiscal-deficit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西国会批准了一项法案，为财政部长费尔南多·哈达德带来了胜利，该法案将有助于增加公共收入，并使他更接近实现 2024 年基本财政赤字（不包括利息支付）为零的承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/brazil-congress-gets-haddad-closer-to-zero-2024-fiscal-deficit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 23:09:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国正在利用缅甸内战摧毁网络诈骗网络</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/china-is-using-myanmar-civil-war-to-destroy-cyber-scam-networks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上个月，一段视频开始在缅甸社交媒体圈流传。视频中，一名自称毕惠军的男子在看似有软垫的牢房里向家人发出严厉警告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/china-is-using-myanmar-civil-war-to-destroy-cyber-scam-networks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 22:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国警告菲律宾关系面临“严重困难”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/china-warns-philippines-relations-face-serious-difficulties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国外交部长王毅告诉菲律宾外长，由于南海紧张局势加剧，两国关系目前面临“严重困难”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-20/china-warns-philippines-relations-face-serious-difficulties</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Dec 2023 17:28:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
